(2876, 'Cody 30 caps.', 'كودي 30 كبسولة', '', '34', 'Cod liver oil+vitamin a+vitamin d', 'Arab caps > golden queen company', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Multivitamins', '', 'Cod liver oil is predominantly manufactured, marketed, and used by the population at large as a general nutraceutical dietary supplement [A27154, A33159, L2872].
